  "body": [
    "Bhai Kishan Singh Parwana was one of the senior students of Giani Hardit Singh Ji of Guru Nanak Vidhya Bhandaar Trust, also known as the Rakab Ganj Sahib Vidhyala. He was a master of many in the sense that he did wonderful Kirtan, Katha and he also wrote and sang many Dharmak Kavtas. Other notable students of Giani Hardit Singh Ji include Giani Dyal Singh, Bhai Chattar Singh, Bhai Mahinder Singh Shah, Bhai Ajit Singh Alankari, Bhai Lal Singh (Meerut) and many more. If anyone has a photograph or more recordings and information of Bhai Kishan Singh Parwana, please contact us."
